snippet.title: Hatsune Miku: VR Future Live - 20 Minute 1st Stage Playthrough [PS4]
snippet.description:
Playing 20 minutes of Hatsune Miku: VR Future Live on Playstation 4. Doing a run through the 1st Stage set of songs. Playstation VR is required to play this software.

Game: Hatsune Miku: VR Future Live
Platform: Playstation 4 (PSVR required) [digital]
Release Date: October 13, 2016
Price: $14.99 per stage (3 stages total), $39.99 for Season Pass (All 3 Stages)
